{"type": "article", "id": 13579, "title": "折叠手工系列花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-17T07:55:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150237Dv6yb7iOAnjCqE8e.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自伦敦的设计工作室 ODDD 推出的一系列花瓶，意在体味 2D 和 3D 之间奇妙的转换。只需要折叠纸张并充气，就可以完成花瓶的手工制作，是不是有点像我们小时候做的手工，不过他们使用的是防水材料，可以真正装上水，插进鲜花。另外还有两款花瓶采用高密度聚乙烯合成纸材质，不可见水，专门为干花设计。另外，花瓶表面还设计了金属箔片，看上去有 “blingbling” 的效果。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/505844910/o2-vase\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141315NlSRbTXtW524PLsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141316fLJVIv1b3hc5jsn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413165BqJhmWAalETKo86.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.82640587\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141317No9wplQsJbXxfhi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141318dFt7JjMozx2wPOZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141318Uwpquvs9myD71gAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141318pdAufycrYekLoQwC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141319XyuNlsqjwToJBIG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}